{"tid":2099213,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Fifa 20 韋根career mode圖文直播","createTime":"2020-07-08T05:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T04:07:08.000Z","uid":108894,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42b2dfd337e013afe7d29104f7dbd20211ddba89","tid":2099213,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"韋根自從2013由英超降班之後就一沉不起，2017年更加跌落英甲，雖然最近回升英冠但實力未足以挑戰升班，韋根班主決定聘任新領隊Rossi，Rossi甫上任第一日就豪言要不但要率隊重返英超，未來更要係英超取得佳績，要同英國乃至世人傳揚韋根小強不死嘅生命力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隊中值得留意嘅球員:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxRLKRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoxRLKRd.jpg&h=0d4d54b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeXnM45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeXnM45.jpg&h=f069e2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPMf663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPMf663.jpg&h=0d02b2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於球隊班費少，買唔到太多球員，因此Rossi決定放眼未來，重金禮聘三位球探，打造以青訓為主嘅球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0EYkss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0EYkss.jpg&h=05a5a8d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱身賽雖然未能奪冠而回取得全額獎金，但由於只係試驗緊陣容同組合，Rossi領隊同高層對球隊仍然有信心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X5kyOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X5kyOO.jpg&h=483a3270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNtVnHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNtVnHa.jpg&h=d0520512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/08/131750_2e91c9e33d35a3a075b9289d1a58912a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F08%2F131750_2e91c9e33d35a3a075b9289d1a58912a.jpg&h=1b5040cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Uvc9nh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Uvc9nh.jpg&h=ebc5e8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而為爭取升班，Rossi借入左Angel Gomes同Kutucu，增強球隊攻力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39QTTPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39QTTPy.jpg&h=1cee674a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPOqKWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPOqKWu.jpg&h=23b8ff99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但增兵工作未完成，韋根仍需要多一名中堅同翼鋒加強球隊陣容深度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyxOHJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyxOHJM.jpg&h=bd05ce56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯賽首場將面對實力不俗嘅有錢球隊卡迪夫城，希望旗開得勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(待續)"},{"pid":"a1cd52252034c3da8c0f85d32d1dabffbd69dbb3","tid":2099213,"uid":29283,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"Cmhk<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce6f6cee68eed1d40c0d39f7ae15991e7233867","tid":2099213,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"大家有咩平靚正球員推薦，得4M班費好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d3a4ca6a96b7abfbc56e4942b711f0e2c92003","tid":2099213,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:29:01.000Z","msg":"巨根精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d106c22280227f43885dea9aeb5d539cf7e350","tid":2099213,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe249e6a10238faed079d287d1a9a015b976616e","tid":2099213,"uid":106027,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202